dct_title_s: Rutgers University, New Jersey, 1946 football schedule
dct_description_sm: Rutgers University's football schedule for 1946. Verso features a location map of Rutgers University showing the vicinity of New Brunswick, New Jersey and routes to the Rutgers Stadium.
